Results: - Proposed IT GRC smart adviser optimizes IT strategies.  
- Simulation results showed similarities with human experts' decisions. || 
Objectives: - Integrate IT and business processes using ITG frameworks.  
- Propose a smart architecture for COBIT process matching. },
